* API :
  ----
    -> an api is just a mechanism to communicate between 2 services or 2 apps

       1. abstraction

       2. standards :  [for state transfers]

            -> approach (REST, GraphqL, SOAP, Socket)
               params
               endpoints
               response  (json, xml)

               REST := ReqEST, (Eg get, post, put, delete, etc..)

* SDK : (Software Dev Kit)
  ---
    -> toolbox of tools/codes that calls API for us.
    -> SDK are available for variety of languages.
